  <brief_title>GLPG0259 Multiple Ascending Dose and Methotrexate Drug-drug Interaction (DDI) in Healthy Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>Double Blind, Placebo Controlled, Dose Ranging and Methotrexate Interaction Study for the Assessment of Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics (PK) of Multiple Oral Doses of GLPG0259 in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
